	(text "Needed for programming\nboot EEPROM\n\nTPS65217 I2C Addrs = 0x24\nEEPROM I2C Addrs = 0x50\n\nNeeds 4 pos 1.27 mm socket\nand cable, e.g., \nSamtec SFSS-04-28-H-06.00-SR."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 16.51 245.11 0)
		(effects
